<h1>Install Web Application on macOS using MS Edge</h1>

<p>To install this web application on macOS using MS Edge, follow these steps:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Open MS Edge on your macOS device.</li>
  <li>Navigate to the website URL of the web application.</li>
  <li>Click on the "..." menu icon in the top-right corner of the browser window.</li>
  <li>From the dropdown menu, select "Install Joy of Rails".</li>
  <li>Follow the prompts to complete the installation process.</li>
  <li>The Joy of Rails icon will now be added as a standalone application.</li>
</ol>

<p>Once the installation is complete, you can access the web application directly from your macOS device's applications or launchpad.</p>
